    dc:description "FIGURES 103–105. Phaeoxantha (P.) laminata (Perty), historical specimens of syn. Megacephala asperula Westwood (MNHN), habitus. 103—♂, 10.2 mm, “Para” [Pará, Brazil]; 104—♂, 9.6 mm, Pebas [Peru]; 105—♀, 9.9 mm, Pebas. Bar = 1 mm." ;
