    dc:description "FIGURES 106–112. Phaeoxantha (P.) laminata (Perty), historical specimen of syn. Megacephala asperulaWestwood (BMNH), ♂. 106—habitus, 9.9 mm; 107—labrum; 108—labels; 109—pronotum; 110—ditto, detail of surface; 111—elytron; 112—ditto, detail of surface. Bars = 1 mm." ;
